data.description: Welcome to your dream home, a recently built 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence where luxury and comfort seamlessly merge. The owners spared no expense in this home with high-end finishes, starting with a modern kitchen featuring quartz countertops, a stylish tile backsplash, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. The downstairs area exudes elegance with high-quality laminate flooring and includes a convenient half bathroom. Natural light floods through the 2'' wood blinds that adorn the windows throughout the house, creating a warm, inviting atmosphere.The upstairs is a haven of comfort with plush carpeting, two full bathrooms for added privacy and convenience, and a luxurious master suite. This private retreat boasts a dual vanity, a standalone shower, and a dedicated toilet room, alongside a generous walk-in closet. Additionally, the upper level houses a versatile bonus loft, perfect for a home office or a cozy den, and two additional bedrooms, offering ample space for family and guests alike.  Step outside to a serene, fully fenced backyard that backs up to peaceful woods, providing a picturesque and private outdoor space. Completing this magnificent home is a two-car garage and a spacious driveway, ensuring ample parking and storage. This property is not just a house; it's a lifestyle offering the perfect blend of luxury, style, and functionality.
